                <h1>Discover the Mighty Wolverine: Nature's Resilient Predator</h1>
                <p>Wolverines are fascinating creatures known for their strength and ferocity. These stocky carnivores thrive in cold northern climates, traversing vast territories in search of food. With powerful limbs and sharp claws, they are adept hunters, often preying on smaller animals. Their tenacity makes them one of nature's feared scavengers, earning their status as a symbol of resilience.</p>
